item.title: [525] Help, run wont work
item.dc:creator: @eld0002 eld0002
item.description:
@eld0002 wrote:

Find your Logger.java, There should be a code that has // next to it
Ill get it for you 1 sec:

synchronized(getClass()) { if(level == Level.DEBUG || level == Level.INFO) { System.out.println(formatMessage(message)); } else { System.err.println(formatMessage(message)); } }

There should be // next to the System Printin’s, just get rid of them and it will work
